data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this nicely updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home located in the desirable city of Port Charlotte. Boasting a generous living space of 1,896 square feet and new roof this year, this residence offers a comfortable and inviting atmosphere for you to call home. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the well-designed split floor plan, providing both privacy and functionality. The high ceilings throughout the home create an open and airy ambiance, enhancing the overall sense of spaciousness. The heart of the home is the inviting living area, where you can relax and unwind with family and friends and enjoy a wood burning fireplace with stone facade'. The large windows and sliding glass doors flood the room with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming environment. Adjacent to the living area, you'll find a dining space that is perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying meals together. The updated kitchen is well-lit and features granite countertops, large breakfast bar with beautiful pendant lighting and storage, new suite of GE stainless steel appliances, pantry closet, ample counter space, plenty of storage for all your culinary needs and overlooks the living area. Prepare delicious meals with ease and enjoy the convenience of a cozy eat-in space making it ideal for quick meals or casual dining. The master bedroom is a true retreat, with a walk-in closets and is complete with its own sliders that open to the lanai area. The master bathroom has been updated with a new dual sink vanity, a walk-in shower, step up to a relaxing soaking tub or enjoy the atrium with coral stone wall and shower . The two additional bedrooms are generously sized and provide comfortable spaces for family members or guests. The second bathroom, also with new vanity, is conveniently located, ensuring everyone's needs are met.  Step outside to discover a private 36 x 12 screened-in lanai that overlooks a large backyard.  This outdoor space offers endless opportunities for relaxation and entertainment. Home also features laundry room w/ utility sink, new roof in 2023, water heater 2023, A/C 2016, updated landscape, wood laminate flooring throughout, new light and ceiling fan fixtures. Situated in Port Charlotte, Florida, this home provides easy access to a variety of amenities, including shopping centers, dining options, parks, and recreational activities. Enjoy the renowned Florida lifestyle with nearby beaches, boating, and fishing opportunities, ensuring that you are never far from the area's natural beauty.
